Actual Effects: Self: Lose Mana (300) <br>
  Target: Receive Mana (100) <br>
Description: This is a mana form of the Pact series. This spell enables you to transfer your mana to another player.<br>
Best used in skeleton form in conjunction with a lifetap DoT, this spell enables you to reduce meditation downtime by topping up mana levels of other players during a fight. <br>
<br>
This spell is best used in emergency situations. Not efficient enough to keep memmed all the time, but could provide a player with enough mana to finish their job.<br>
